OL,3,CBanned taxi drivers are using licence
OL,4,Cloophole, says council
OL,6,FNorth Somerset Councillor Mike Solomon
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've seen a lot of complaints
OL,8,Frecently that anybody who needs a taxi
OL,9,Flicence that can't get one from our
OL,10,Fcouncil because we are very stringent
OL,11,Fin our tests, can apply to
OL,12,FWolverhampton and very easily get that
OL,13,Flicence."
OL,15,FWeston-super-Mare councillor Catherine
OL,16,FGibbons said: "When I was in Liverpool
OL,17,Frecently at a conference, it was a
OL,18,Fmajor complaint amongst taxi drivers
OL,19,Fthere that half their taxis are
OL,20,Flicensed in Wolverhampton as well."
