OL,3,CBanned taxi drivers are using licence
OL,4,Cloophole, says council
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the City of
OL,7,FWolverhampton Council has said they
OL,8,Fhave "never actively encouraged
OL,9,Fapplications from drivers outside the
OL,10,Fcity".
OL,12,FThey said: "Existing legislation
OL,13,Frequires that if an application is
OL,14,Fsubmitted and requirements are met,
OL,15,Fthen the application must be granted.
OL,16,FThere is no lawful basis to refuse an
OL,17,Fapplication from someone who lives
OL,18,Fsomewhere else in the country."
