OL,3,CBanned taxi drivers are using licence
OL,4,Cloophole, says council
OL,6,FThe council said they do not gain
OL,7,Ffinancially from issuing licenses, and
OL,8,Fthat its taxi driver training program
OL,9,Fhad "some of the highest standards in
OL,10,Fthe country" with DBS checks on taxi
OL,11,Fdrivers performed by the council every
OL,12,Fday.
OL,14,FThe council spokesperson said: "There
OL,15,Fis no evidence to suggest any taxi
OL,16,Fdrivers have had their license revoked
OL,17,Fby North Somerset. We have spoken with
OL,18,FNorth Somerset council and confirmed a
OL,19,Fsingle case involving a driver who was
OL,20,Flicensed by both councils.
