OL,3,CBanned taxi drivers are using licence
OL,4,Cloophole, says council
OL,6,F"In August 2023, the driver was found
OL,7,Fguilty of driving without due care and
OL,8,Fattention.
OL,10,F"After immediately informing City of
OL,11,FWolverhampton Council of the offence,
OL,12,Fhe was called to a hearing before a
OL,13,Flicensing manager. At the hearing he
OL,14,Fwas ordered to complete a training
OL,15,Fprogramme and pass a further driving
OL,16,Ftest to retain his license.
